org.dlw.ai.blackboard.knowledge
Enum KnowledgeSourceType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<KnowledgeSourceType>
      org.dlw.ai.blackboard.knowledge.KnowledgeSourceType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KnowledgeSourceType>
public enum KnowledgeSourceType
extends java.lang.Enum<KnowledgeSourceType>

This enum provides enumerated types for specifically implemented knowledge sources to support the default blackboard model implementation. Please note that this is an implementation enumerated type and should not be considered API. These enumerations are specific to the default implementation.

Version:
1.0.0-RC
Author:
David L. Whitehurst
